[agent] Health endpoints:
[agent] - /health: Basic liveness check
[agent] - /health?ready=1: Readiness check (considers cluster status)
[agent] - /_status/vars: Prometheus metrics including under-replicated ranges
[agent] Recovery process:
[agent] 1. Readiness probe fails for one pod
[agent] 2. Pod removed from Service (no new connections)
[agent] 3. Operator waits for readiness to recover
[agent] 4. Pod rejoins cluster and health checks pass
